      <hr /><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1><span>788</span> - <span>Complex Linking Entry Data</span><span> (NR)</span></h1>
      <hr />
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Authority - full</div>
      <div class="datename">October 2014</div>
